title: Print, Interior View, Augustin Daly's Theater, New York, 1879
title_raw: Interior View, Augustin Daly's Theater, New York
medium: Black ink on heavy white paper
dimensions: 271 X 322 mm ( plate line), 290 X 344 mm (paper)
description: Horizontal rectangle.  View of the interior, taken from the first balcony, looking toward the orchestra and the stage.  Three tiers of boxes flank the stage.  A play in progress, showing details of a stage set.  Title below.
